    <h1>Research</h1>

    <h2>Job Market Paper</h2>
    <div class="paper">
      <div class="paper-title">The Impacts of Job Security and Tenure Reforms on Teacher and Student Outcomes</div>
      <div class="meta">Wilfried Adohinzin · 2025 · <span class="muted">Fuzzy RD & DiD; Peru administrative data</span></div>
      <div class="tags">
        <span class="pill">Labor</span>
        <span class="pill">Development</span>
        <span class="pill">Education</span>
      </div>
      <p>I study merit‑based job security for public‑sector teachers. Offering permanent contracts reduces exits, especially among high‑quality teachers, and modestly improves student learning; effects are weaker in rural and low‑SES settings. Composition changes increase average teacher quality.</p>
      <p>
        <a class="btn" href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1NWpzQXV1p54IkEfSPVU18SVYPmwyqOeW/view?usp=drive_link">Paper (PDF)</a>
        <a class="btn" href="#">Slides</a>
        <a class="btn" href="#">BibTeX</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>Working Papers</h2>
    <div class="paper">
      <div class="paper-title">The Effects of Immigration Enforcement on the Rental Market: Evidence from the Secure Communities Program</div>
      <div class="meta">2025 · <span class="muted">Event study; US counties</span></div>
      <p>Enhanced interior immigration enforcement decreases rental prices in targeted areas, consistent with out‑migration and demand reallocation.</p>
      <p>
        <a class="btn" href="#">Paper (PDF)</a>
        <a class="btn" href="#">BibTeX</a>
